  <brief_title>Effect of Water Intake and Water Restriction on Total Kidney Volume in Autosomal Dominant Polycystic Kidney Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Water Intake and Water Restriction on Total Kidney Volume in Autosomal Dominant Polycystic Kidney: The HYDRA Study</official_title>
